  <brief_title>Methylphenidate in the Treatment of Cocaine Dependent Patients With Adult Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder - 5</brief_title>
  <official_title>Methyphendidate in the Treatment of Cocaine Dependent Patients With Adult ADHD</official_title>
  <sponsors>
